{"word":"κάρ 2","slug":"κάρ 2","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n53245\" key=\"ka/r2\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\">*<orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κάρ</orth> (A), a word of uncertain gender, nom. form, and meaning, typifying what is worthless, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τίω δέ μιν ἐν κᾰρὸς αἴσῃ</foreign> I value him at <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">α . . </foreign>'<sense id=\"n53245.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">s worth</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:378\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.378</biblScope> </bibl>: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">καρός</foreign> is variously expld. by <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> </bibl> Byz. etc. ap. Sch., e.g.as <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">κηρός</ref> </xr> or as pr.n. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Καρός</foreign>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n53245.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">κάρα, ἐπὶ κάρ</ref> </xr> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">head</tr_>-long (nisi junctim scrib.), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:392\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.392</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀνὰ κάρ</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">upwards</tr_>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> </bibl> ap. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Gal.\">Gal.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.79</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}